      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for a driver who values mechanical reliability over aesthetic perfection. The engine starts up and runs consistently, though it would benefit from a routine service to optimize performance. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches and minor dents, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery and some faded plastic trim. All major systems are functional, making this a dependable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little elbow grease to bring it back to its former glory.",
