      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated dual-VANOS system. This specimen boasts a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, delivering visceral mechanical feedback. The chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral G-loads. Meticulously maintained with zero rod-bearing issues and a pristine valvetrain, this vehicle retains its original factory tolerances and concours-level exterior finish. A definitive example for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
